query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `agents` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `integrationId` int NOT NULL,
  `name` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `role` enum('primary','backup','loadbalance') DEFAULT 'primary' NOT NULL,
  `status` enum('online','busy','offline','error') DEFAULT 'offline' NOT NULL,
  `currentLoad` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `maxLoad` int DEFAULT 10 NOT NULL,
  `lastActiveAt` timestamp,
  `failureCount` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `successCount` int DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  CONSTRAINT `agents_id` PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
);
